flowchart TD
    A[Start: α at time n] --> B[Calculate explicit fluxes F]
    B --> C[Apply limiting to fluxes]
    C --> D{Check boundedness?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Accept fluxes]
    D -->|No| F[Apply correction]
    F --> G[Iteration count < nIter?]
    G -->|Yes| C
    G -->|No| E
    E --> H[Update α to time n+1]
    H --> I[End]
    
    subgraph "MULES Parameters"
        J[nIter: Maximum limiter iterations]
        K[Default: nIter = 3]
    end
    
    style J fill:#fff3e0
    style K fill:#fff3e0